snippet.title: Superflight Launch Trailer - Wingsuit Highscore Game
snippet.description:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/732430/Superflight/

Superflight is an intense, easy to learn wingsuit game with an infinite number of beautiful procedurally generated maps. In this video, we'll explain everything you need to know about the game in 3 minutes. 

Website: https://superflightgame.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/_grizzlygames
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SuperFlightGame

Developed as part of the GameDesign Bachelor program @ HTW-Berlin: https://twitter.com/gamedesign_htw
